---
// Pricing.astro
---

<div class="title-section">
  <div class="decorative-elements">
    <div class="gradient-bg"></div>
    <div class="top-line"></div>
    <div class="bottom-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <h1>Naši paketi i <span class="highlight">Usluge</span></h1>
    <p>
      Izaberite iz našeg sveobuhvatnog asortimana vozačkih usluga prilagođenih
      vašim potrebama.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="pricing-container">
  <div class="pricing-card">
    <div class="pricing-header">
      <h2>Teorijska obuka</h2>
      <p>40 časova</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-amount">RSD 16.000</div>
    <p class="pricing-description">
      Plaćanje možete izvršiti u toku obuke gotovinom, čekovima građana na više
      mesečnih rata, putem administrativne zabrane ili bankarskim kreditom. Ceo
      iznos možete platiti u više MESEČNIH RATA ili odjednom. Način plaćanja i
      izbor broja rata je samo Vaš izbor i odlučujete Vi.
    </p>
    <p class="pricing-per-hour">⊗ Cena po času – 400 RSD</p>
    <button class="pricing-cta">Zakaži termin</button>
  </div>

  <div class="pricing-card">
    <div class="pricing-header">
      <h2>Praktična obuka</h2>
      <p>40 časova</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-amount">RSD 60.000</div>
    <p class="pricing-description">
      Plaćanje možete izvršiti u toku obuke gotovinom, čekovima građana na više
      mesečnih rata, putem administrativne zabrane ili bankarskim kreditom. Ceo
      iznos možete platiti u više MESEČNIH RATA ili odjednom. Način plaćanja i
      izbor broja rata je samo Vaš izbor i odlučujete Vi.
    </p>
    <p class="pricing-per-hour">⊗ Cena po času – 1500 RSD</p>
    <button class="pricing-cta">Zakaži termin</button>
  </div>

  <div class="pricing-card pricing-card-small">
    <div class="pricing-header pricing-header-dark">
      <h2>Teorijski ispit</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-amount">RSD 6.000</div>
    <button class="pricing-cta">Zakaži termin</button>
  </div>

  <div class="pricing-card pricing-card-small">
    <div class="pricing-header pricing-header-dark">
      <h2>Praktični ispit</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-amount">RSD 6.000</div>
    <button class="pricing-cta">Zakaži termin</button>
  </div>
</div>
<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
    const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.pricing-cta');

    buttons.forEach((button) => {
      button.addEventListener('click', function () {
        window.location.href = '/contact'; // Prilagodi URL prema kontakt stranici
      });
    });
  });
</script>
<style>
  .pricing-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 4rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 10px;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    color: #4b5563;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2c3149;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .highlight {
    color: #eab308;
  }
  .pricing-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(44, 49, 73, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    /* background-color: rgba(44, 49, 73, 0.05); */
    /* backdrop-filter: blur(10px); */
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .pricing-card-small {
    min-height: unset;
  }

  .pricing-header {
    background-color: #2c3149;
    color: white;
    padding: 15px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-header-dark {
    background-color: #212539;
  }

  .pricing-header h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .pricing-header p {
    margin: 5px 0 0;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .pricing-amount {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 10px;
    color: #2c3149;
  }

  .pricing-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 0 15px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #2c3149;
  }

  .pricing-per-hour {
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #2c3149;
    padding: 10px 15px;
  }

  .pricing-cta {
    background-color: #2c3149;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 16px;
    margin: auto 0px 20px;
    width: 50%;
    max-width: 240px;
    align-self: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    border-radius: 19px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3sease;

  .pricing-cta:hover {
    /* background-color: #2c3252; */
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  /* Mobile Responsiveness */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .pricing-amount {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .pricing-header h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .pricing-card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02) translateY(-3px);
    }
  }
</style>
